---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy – ohara.systems"
  description="Privacy policy for ohara.systems in accordance with GDPR"
  lang="en"
  canonicalPath="/en/privacy"
  alternatePath="/datenschutz"
>
  <section class="px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="space-y-8">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">Responsible Party</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            Responsible for data processing on this website:<br />
            ohara.systems<br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:ai@ohara.systems" class="text-[#38bdf8] hover:text-[#7dd3fc] transition-colors">ai@ohara.systems</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">General Information on Data Processing</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            This is a static website. No user accounts are created, no forms collect personal data,
            and no server-side processing of personal data takes place. The processing of personal
            data is limited to the technically necessary delivery of the website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">Hosting / Cloudflare Pages</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            This website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. When you visit this website, Cloudflare
            automatically processes technically necessary data, in particular your IP address,
            in order to deliver the website content to your browser. This is technically required
            for the operation of the website and is based on Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest
            in the reliable provision of the website).
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            For more information about data protection at Cloudflare, please refer to the
            <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#38bdf8] hover:text-[#7dd3fc] transition-colors">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">SSL Encryption</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            This website uses SSL encryption for security purposes and to protect the transmission
            of data. You can recognize an encrypted connection by the address bar of the browser
            changing from "http://" to "https://" and by the lock icon in your browser bar.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">No Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            This website does not use cookies. Neither first-party nor third-party cookies are set.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">No Analytics Tools</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            This website does not use any analytics or tracking tools. No usage statistics are
            collected and no user behavior is analyzed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">External Links</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            This website contains links to external third-party websites. We are not responsible
            for the privacy practices of these external websites. Please refer to their respective
            privacy policies for more information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">Rights of the Data Subject</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white/50 leading-relaxed space-y-1 mt-3">
            <li>Right of access to your personal data stored by us (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to rectification of inaccurate data (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to erasure of your data (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to object to processing (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            To exercise your rights, please contact:
            <a href="mailto:ai@ohara.systems" class="text-[#38bdf8] hover:text-[#7dd3fc] transition-colors">ai@ohara.systems</a>
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            <strong class="text-white/70">Note:</strong> This website does not process any personal data itself.
            No user accounts are created, no forms are evaluated, and no tracking data is collected.
            Therefore, we generally cannot provide you with stored personal data, as none exists.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            The only means of contact is via email. Email communication is stored on servers operated by
            Strato (STRATO AG, Berlin). Their
            <a href="https://www.strato.de/datenschutz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#38bdf8] hover:text-[#7dd3fc] transition-colors">privacy policy</a> applies.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mt-3">
            You also have the right to lodge a complaint with a data protection supervisory
            authority regarding the processing of your personal data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-3">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to update this privacy policy to ensure it always complies with
            current legal requirements or to implement changes to our services in the privacy
            policy. The new privacy policy will apply to your next visit.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
